CBRE is pleased to offer 680 Boundary Road, Richlands a modern logistics facility within Brisbanes western corridor. 

+  Fully Leased with a WALE of 3.7 Years (as at 1 March 2019)
+  Passing net income of $1,438,928 per annum
+  21,985sqm Regular shaped General Industrial site
+  12,633sqm Dual tenanted modern logistics facility  
+  Dual driveway access allowing for full drive around capability
+  Warehouse accessed via multiple on grade roller doors and loading docks
+  Good concrete hardstand areas for truck movement and container set down
+  Warehouse has 9m canter lever awnings & ESFR sprinkler system
+  Ample car parking and fully fenced and secure site

Richlands is approximately 14 kilometres south-west of the Brisbane CBD and offers direct access to the Ipswich Motorway and Centenary Freeway.

The property is offered For Sale via an Expressions of Interest campaign Closing 4pm (AEDT) Thursday 28th of March
